  <reg:filed>January 15, 1974</reg:filed>
  <reg:acttitle>Public Service Labour Relations Act</reg:acttitle>
  <reg:title>Public Service Labour Relations Regulations</reg:title>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e22" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Regulation title</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>These regulations may be cited as the Public Service Labour Relations Regulations.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e34">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Regulations and forms adopted</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The regulations made and forms prescribed under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96244_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Labour Relations Code</in:doc></bcl:link> are hereby made applicable to all applications, proceedings or complaints before the board under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96388_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Public Service Labour Relations Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e52">
      <bcl:marginalnote>"Employer" defined</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The "employer" referred to in the regulations made under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96244_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Labour Relations Code</in:doc></bcl:link> shall be for purposes of this Act the "government" as defined in the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96388_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Public Service Labour Relations Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e70">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Signatures on documents</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>4</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>Applications, replies or other documents filed on behalf of the "government" under these regulations shall be signed by a person duly authorized in writing by the Public Service Commission to sign on its behalf.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96388_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Public Service Labour Relations Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 388, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: sectionÂ 19]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
</reg:regulation>